    note right of Unregistered
        getMBeansFromURL() throws IllegalStateException
        when MLet is not registered with an MBeanServer.
        postRegister(true) transitions to Registered.
        postRegister(false) stays Unregistered.
    end note

    note right of Registered
        getMBeansFromURL() is only valid in this state.
        postDeregister() returns to Unregistered state.
    end note
